          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "According to New Jersey State Police, Blonday J. Acosta was one of “numerous” drivers trying to flee the scene of illegal street racing in Port Norris Station when officers arrived. One of the cruisers maneuvered his car to block a green Honda Civic from escaping, which police say Acosta was driving. Instead of stopping, Acosta ",
